<Layout>
  <p class="flex text-lg md:text-sm relative z-50 mt-32">
    <span class="grow">Audemars Piguet</span>
    <span class="grow hidden md:inline"> Mémorendum Volontriat </span>
    <span class="grow hidden md:inline">
      DA, identité visuelle, Illustration, design editorial
    </span>
    <span>2022</span>
  </p>
  <Image src={catImage} alt="cat image" class="mt-5" />
  <p class="text-xl mt-3">
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nulla ut rem nobis
    aspernatur, numquam consectetur officiis, quas quod facilis dolores dolor
    dolorem explicabo nostrum ducimus, eligendi non natus aperiam error?
  </p>
  <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-x-5 mt-10">
    <div class="md:col-span-2 md:col-start-2 mb-3">
      <Image src={catImage} alt="cat image" />
      <p class="text-xs mt-1">Flyer format 15 recto/verso</p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-2 mb-3">
      <Image src={catImage} alt="cat image" />
      <p class="text-xs mt-1">Flyer format 15 recto/verso</p>
